"title": "7758: preachers, call of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "7758: preachers, call of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God declares his word through called and anointed preachers. He overcomes their reluctance, helps their weakness, authorises their message and confirms the truth of what they declare.</p>\n<h2>God's call of preachers</h2>\n<h3>It is not dependent upon background</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos7:14-Amos7:15\">AMO 7:14–7:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:1-Jer1:5\">JER 1:1–1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:18-Matt4:20\">MAT 4:18–4:20</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:16-Mark1:19\">MRK 1:16–1:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:1-Luke5:11\">LUK 5:1–5:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:10-Acts9:16\">ACT 9:10–9:16</a></p>\n<h3>It is not dependent upon ability</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:10-Exod4:12\">EXO 4:10–4:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:6-Jer1:9\">JER 1:6–1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:13\">ACT 4:13</a></p>\n<h3>It is not dependent upon willingness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:13\">EXO 4:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah1:1-Jonah1:3\">JON 1:1–1:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:1-Acts9:6\">ACT 9:1–9:6</a></p>\n<h3>It is a matter of God's sovereign choice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:4-Jer1:5\">JER 1:4–1:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:1-Isa49:6\">ISA 49:1–49:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek2:1-Ezek2:5\">EZK 2:1–2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos7:14-Amos7:15\">AMO 7:14–7:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:18-Luke4:19\">LUK 4:18–4:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa61:1-Isa61:2\">ISA 61:1–61:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:15\">GAL 1:15</a></p>\n<h2>God's commissioning of preachers</h2>\n<h3>They are commissioned to declare God's word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:1\">EZK 3:1</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:13-Rom10:15\">ROM 10:13–10:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:9\">JER 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah3:1-Jonah3:2\">JON 3:1–3:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:18-Matt28:20\">MAT 28:18–28:20</a></p>\n<h3>They are to declare God's word with authority</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus2:15\">TIT 2:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:9-Jer1:10\">JER 1:9–1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:14-Mark3:15\">MRK 3:14–3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke9:1-Luke9:2\">LUK 9:1–9:2</a></p>\n<h3>They are to declare God's word without fear</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:7-Jer1:8\">JER 1:7–1:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek2:3-Ezek2:7\">EZK 2:3–2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek3:7-Ezek3:9\">EZK 3:7–3:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:27-Acts5:29\">ACT 5:27–5:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:6-2Tim1:8\">2TI 1:6–1:8</a></p>\n<h2>God's constraint upon preachers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:16\">1CO 9:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:8-Jer20:9\">JER 20:8–20:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:18-Acts4:20\">ACT 4:18–4:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:14-Rom1:15\">ROM 1:14–1:15</a></p>\n<h2>God's confirmation of his call upon preachers</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:3\">ACT 14:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod4:1-Exod4:9\">EXO 4:1–4:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:17-1Kgs17:24\">1KI 17:17–17:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:20\">MRK 16:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:29-Acts4:31\">ACT 4:29–4:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor2:4\">1CO 2:4</a></p>",
